definitions.input_prompt:
Compute the budget and fit scores for the following accommodation options. Apply the deterministic scoring rules. Return raw JSON only.

Request:
{
  "budget_per_night": 180,
  "options": [
    {
      "option_id": "stay_001",
      "name": "Hotel Bairro Alto",
      "price_per_night": 165,
      "mobility_score": 0.84,
      "weather_score": 0.88
    },
    {
      "option_id": "stay_002",
      "name": "Hotel Oriente",
      "price_per_night": 210,
      "mobility_score": 0.71,
      "weather_score": 0.88
    },
    {
      "option_id": "stay_003",
      "name": "Hotel Cascais",
      "price_per_night": 140,
      "mobility_score": 0.42,
      "weather_score": 0.88
    }
  ]
}

Evaluate the mobility of the following accommodation options. Use Google Maps tools to geocode locations and compute routes. Return raw JSON only.

Request:
{
  "destination": "Lisbonne",
  "points_of_interest": ["city_center", "airport"],
  "options": [
    {
      "option_id": "stay_001",
      "name": "Hotel Bairro Alto",
      "location_text": "Bairro Alto, Lisbonne"
    },
    {
      "option_id": "stay_002",
      "name": "Hotel Oriente",
      "location_text": "Parque das Nações, Lisbonne"
    },
    {
      "option_id": "stay_003",
      "name": "Hotel Cascais",
      "location_text": "Cascais, région de Lisbonne"
    }
  ]
}

Find accommodation options for the following request. Do NOT answer from memory — use the search tools to retrieve live results. Return raw JSON only.

Request:
{
  "destination": "Lisbonne",
  "check_in": "2026-05-12",
  "check_out": "2026-05-15",
  "budget_per_night": 180,
  "preferences": {
    "near_city_center": true
  }
}
